### Creer un commentaire
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Merci pour la mise a jour, je valide cette tache.",
  "taskId": "{{taskId}}",
  "authorId": "{{authorId}}"
}

### Creer un commentaire - retour a faire
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Il faut retravailler le CSS. Voir les wireframes Figma.",
  "taskId": "{{taskId}}",
  "authorId": "{{authorId}}"
}

### Lister les commentaires
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Recuperer un commentaire par ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Modifier un commentaire
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "J'ai pris en compte tes retours, merci!"
}

### Supprimer un commentaire
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test erreur: task invalide -> 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Test",
  "taskId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "authorId": "{{authorId}}"
}

### Test erreur: author invalide -> 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Test",
  "taskId": "{{taskId}}",
  "authorId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}
